754
01:19:06,407 --> 01:19:08,368
The <i>Times:</i> "Blue bomb buzzes
Metropolis."

755
01:19:08,534 --> 01:19:09,577
<i>The Planet:</i>

756
01:19:09,744 --> 01:19:12,830
We have the story of the century here.

757
01:19:12,997 --> 01:19:14,874
I want the name of
