761
01:19:24,842 --> 01:19:26,886
Exactly how would you know that,
Kent?

762
01:19:27,053 --> 01:19:28,513
Um....

763
01:19:29,347 --> 01:19:31,099
Just a first impression.

764
01:19:31,266 --> 01:19:33,851
Who's talking cheap?
I'll make him partner if I have to.

765
01:19:34,018 --> 01:19:35,561
- Right?
- Right, chief.

766
01:19:37,188 --> 01:19:38,606
I want the real story.

767
01:19:38,773 --> 01:19:41,192
I want the inside dope on this guy.

768
01:19:41,359 --> 01:19:45,029
Has he got a family? Where does he live?
What does the <i>S</i> stand for...

769
01:19:45,196 --> 01:19:47,532
LOIS: " <i>Tonight at eight. Your place.
