770
01:19:47,699 --> 01:19:48,783
How does he fly?

771
01:19:48,950 --> 01:19:50,451
<i>A friend."</i>

772
01:19:53,746 --> 01:19:56,249
Tony, who is he?
Mike, what's his name?

773
01:19:56,416 --> 01:19:58,751
What's he got hidden under
that cape? Batteries?

774
01:19:58,918 --> 01:20:00,295
Why did he show up last night?

775
01:20:00,461 --> 01:20:02,714
Dick, where does he come from?

776
01:20:02,880 --> 01:20:04,090
Does he have a girlfriend?

777
01:20:06,676 --> 01:20:08,303
