778
01:20:08,469 --> 01:20:11,306
Now, listen to me.
I tell you, boys and girls...

779
01:20:11,472 --> 01:20:13,474
...whichever one of you
gets it out of him...

780
01:20:13,683 --> 01:20:16,561
