802
01:21:52,490 --> 01:21:54,409
Well, not yet, thank goodness.

803
01:21:56,661 --> 01:21:59,247
Would you like a glass of wine?

804
01:21:59,414 --> 01:22:01,582
No, thanks. I never drink when I fly.

805
01:22:02,917 --> 01:22:04,252
Nice place.

806
01:22:04,419 --> 01:22:07,588
Oh, thank you. Thank you.

807
01:22:07,880 --> 01:22:10,675
