01:22:20,852 --> 01:22:22,437
No. No, I'm not.

812
01:22:23,354 --> 01:22:25,106
Do you have a girlfriend?

813
01:22:25,314 --> 01:22:29,318
No, I don't, but if I did, Miss Lane,
