816
01:22:39,829 --> 01:22:41,622
You don't want anyone to
know how old-- Okay.

817
01:22:41,831 --> 01:22:44,542
How big are you? How tall are you?

818
01:22:44,709 --> 01:22:47,044
- About six-four.
