819
01:22:47,211 --> 01:22:51,132
- And how much do you weigh?
- Around 2, 225.

820
01:22:51,716 --> 01:22:54,135
TWO-- 225?

821
01:22:56,387 --> 01:22:57,972
Hm.

822
01:22:59,140 --> 01:23:03,436
Well, I assume, then, that...

