862
01:25:22,033 --> 01:25:25,119
You're gonna end up fighting
every elected official in this country.

863
01:25:25,286 --> 01:25:27,288
I'm sure you don't really mean that, Lois.

864
01:25:27,496 --> 01:25:28,539
I don't believe this.

865
01:25:28,706 --> 01:25:29,749
- Lois?
- Hm?

866
01:25:30,291 --> 01:25:32,126
I never lie.

867
01:25:33,878 --> 01:25:35,087
Oh.

868
01:25:36,505 --> 01:25:37,923
Um....

869
01:25:38,633 --> 01:25:40,051
Uh-- Oh.

870
01:25:40,217 --> 01:25:43,471
- Just how fast do you fly, by the way?
- I don't know, really.

871
01:25:43,638 --> 01:25:46,223
You know, I never actually
bothered to time myself.

872
01:25:46,390 --> 01:25:48,559
- Say...

873
01:25:49,644 --> 01:25:51,479
...why don't we find out?

874
01:25:51,646 --> 01:25:54,065
