01:31:15,344 --> 01:31:16,929
<i>You belong in the sky.</i>

911
01:31:19,139 --> 01:31:20,557
<i>You and I...</i>

912
01:31:22,267 --> 01:31:24,645
<i>...could belong to each other.</i>

913
01:31:27,147 --> 01:31:29,274
<i>If you need a friend...</i>

914
01:31:32,361 --> 01:31:34,780
<i>...I'm the one to fly to.</i>

915
01:31:38,742 --> 01:31:40,995
<i>If you need to be loved...</i>

916
01:31:42,579 --> 01:31:44,581
<i>...here I am.</i>

917
01:31:45,457 --> 01:31:47,584
<i>Read my mind.</i>

918
01:32:08,939 --> 01:32:11,150
Oh, we forgot to time ourselves.

919
01:32:11,316 --> 01:32:12,359
Uh-huh.

920
01:32:12,526 --> 01:32:14,820
Oh, well, maybe next time.

921
01:32:15,529 --> 01:32:16,947
Oh.

922
01:32:23,954 --> 01:32:26,165
- You okay?
- Uh-huh.

923
01:32:27,916 --> 01:32:30,335
Well, good night.

924
01:32:30,794 --> 01:32:33,005
Oh, good night.

925
01:32:37,634 --> 01:32:40,220
What a super man.

926
01:32:45,726 --> 01:32:47,978
